LME copper nudges higher in late trading . LME copper was barely firmer in late inter - office trading on Thursday evening . At 1800 GMT , three months was indicated at $ 2 , 364 / 67 , up a touch from it $ 2 , 360 kerb close . After the weak kerb close , prices were expected to consolidate in thin activity on Friday ahead of the three - day weekend in Britain . Nearby support was pegged at $ 2 , 350 with first resistance at $ 2 , 380 . Scant movement was seen in the other metals . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 - 8065 
